==外界评价==
=== 正面 ===
一般人对《易中天中华史》持肯定态度，代表有该书出版方社长。<ref>{{cite news |author=中华读书报 |title=《易中天中华史》引争议 |url=http://www.gmw.cn/guoxue/2013-05/30/content_7805103.htm |accessdate=2014-12-18 |newspaper= |date=2013-05-30 |archive-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419120752/http://www.gmw.cn/guoxue/2013-05/30/content_7805103.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 负面 ===
部分人质疑中华历史只有三千七百年的说法。丁怀超表示否定并称易中天精神发生问题。<ref>{{cite news |author=京华时报 |title=易中天被指"精神有问题" 回应：八年之后见分晓 |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/newmedia/2013-05/17/c_115806481.htm |accessdate=2014-12-18 |newspaper= |date=2013-05-17 |archive-date=2016-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701065012/http://news.xinhuanet.com/newmedia/2013-05/17/c_115806481.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
<br>也有人批评称他无法自立于史书丛林，本人则回应不介意怎么说。<ref>{{cite news |author=中国新闻网 |title=易中天写中华史遭质疑 回应：不介意别人怎么说 |url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/zhongguoxiandaishi/detail_2013_11/16/31312074_0.shtml |accessdate=2014-12-18 |newspaper= |date=2013-11-16 |archive-date=2013-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131122042732/http://news.ifeng.com/history/zhongguoxiandaishi/detail_2013_11/16/31312074_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
=== 中立 ===
作家[[葛红兵|葛红兵]]表示该作品需要等待完结之后才更适合作定论。<ref>{{cite news |author=羊城晚报 |title=葛红兵谈《易中天中华史》：写完后再作定论 |url=http://www.huaxia.com/zhwh/whrw/rd/2013/06/3391168.html |accessdate=2014-12-18 |newspaper= |date=2013-06-24 |archive-date=2014-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922090748/http://huaxia.com/zhwh/whrw/rd/2013/06/3391168.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
